  "title": "Marketing Officer/ Executive (IT, Technology Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p><p><ul><li>Consolidate sales forecasts submitted by Account Managers during weekly sales meetings.</li><li>Create and source advertising, promotional, and sales enablement materials, including festive gifts for customers.</li><li>Handle incoming sales enquiries and route them to the relevant Account Managers.</li><li>Review and analyse sales data to identify trends and enhance overall performance.</li><li>Prepare sales reports and presentations for vendors.</li><li>Coordinate with vendors on sponsorships, ensuring successful event execution and achievement of all KPIs.</li><li>Maintain and enhance the company website and social media platforms, and work with Digital Marketing to review monthly SEO traffic and engagement reports.</li><li>Generate and follow up on sales leads from various channels.</li><li>Manage marketing co-op fund claims and administer vendor product rebate programmes.</li><li>Oversee reseller partnership renewals, including tracking sales and technical certification requirements.</li></ul></p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><p><ul><li>Diploma in Business or Marketing.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of working experience as marketing role.</li><li>Excellent communication and presentation skills</li></ul></p></p><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p><p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p><p><br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
